{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/eng/frontend/19-08-28/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"displaying-fullcalendar\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#displaying-fullcalendar\" aria-label=\"displaying fullcalendar permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Displaying FullCalendar</h3>\n<p>Before diving into detailed usage, let's start by displaying FullCalendar on the screen. This post explains <strong>how to display FullCalendar using script tags</strong>. If you want to use an ES6 build system instead, please refer to <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/initialize-es6\">this guide</a>.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Download FullCalendar using <code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save @fullcalendar/core @fullcalendar/daygrid</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create an HTML file and paste in the <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/initialize-globals\">test code</a>. Make sure to set the href paths correctly.</p>\n<p>In my case, since I created the HTML file outside the node_modules folder, I modified the paths like this: href='./node_modules/@fullcalendar/core/main.css'.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Open the HTML file in a browser, and the calendar will be displayed as follows:</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/21b4d/19-08-28-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.15789473684211%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/15813/19-08-28-1.webp 190w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/1cdb2/19-08-28-1.webp 380w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/9046c/19-08-28-1.webp 760w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/c89f9/19-08-28-1.webp 1140w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/af3f0/19-08-28-1.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/a2d4f/19-08-28-1.png 190w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3f520/19-08-28-1.png 380w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3c051/19-08-28-1.png 760w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/b5cea/19-08-28-1.png 1140w,\n/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/21b4d/19-08-28-1.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/d91c0181faf14310fa2f7863c1f242e8/3c051/19-08-28-1.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"plugins\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#plugins\" aria-label=\"plugins permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugins</h3>\n<p>If you want more features beyond the basic setup, install plugins and add the desired ones to the <em>'plugins'</em> array. You can check the list of plugins provided by FullCalendar <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/plugin-index\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Install a plugin using <code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save @fullcalendar/'plugin-name'</code>, then add the following code to your HTML file. (For now, I added the interaction and dayGrid plugins to enable the dateClick feature.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/core/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/daygrid/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'./node_modules/@fullcalendar/interaction/main.js'</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">dateClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Clicked on: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>As a result, clicking on a date cell will display an alert dialog.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/21b4d/19-08-28-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.6842105263158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/15813/19-08-28-2.webp 190w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/1cdb2/19-08-28-2.webp 380w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/9046c/19-08-28-2.webp 760w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/c89f9/19-08-28-2.webp 1140w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/af3f0/19-08-28-2.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/a2d4f/19-08-28-2.png 190w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3f520/19-08-28-2.png 380w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3c051/19-08-28-2.png 760w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/b5cea/19-08-28-2.png 1140w,\n/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/21b4d/19-08-28-2.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/32a2e21fc21b5e26ff8b9180fbcd17b7/3c051/19-08-28-2.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"handler\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#handler\" aria-label=\"handler permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Handler</h3>\n<p>To understand why the alert dialog appeared, you need to know about Handlers.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token function-variable function\">dateClick</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Clicked on: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>A handler is a type of option, but specifically one that defines a function called whenever a particular event occurs. In the code above, the <code class=\"language-text\">dateClick: function(info){...}</code> part is the handler, so the corresponding function was executed when a dateClick event occurred.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'dateClick'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">info</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'clicked on '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dateStr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>You can also dynamically add handlers using the on and off methods, as shown above. Besides handlers, you can also control the calendar using FullCalendar's built-in methods -- see the <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/Calendar-prev\">reference</a> for details.</p>\n<h3 id=\"event-options\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#event-options\" aria-label=\"event options permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Event Options</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> calendar <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FullCalendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Calendar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>calendarEl<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'dayGrid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'interaction'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token literal-property property\">events</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">title</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Test1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">start</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-22'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">end</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-24'</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">id</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">title</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Test2'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">start</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-21'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token literal-property property\">end</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2019-08-23'</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>I added an events option and entered the events in an array of objects. Let's check the calendar.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/21b4d/19-08-28-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.10526315789475%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/15813/19-08-28-3.webp 190w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/1cdb2/19-08-28-3.webp 380w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/9046c/19-08-28-3.webp 760w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/c89f9/19-08-28-3.webp 1140w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/af3f0/19-08-28-3.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/a2d4f/19-08-28-3.png 190w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3f520/19-08-28-3.png 380w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3c051/19-08-28-3.png 760w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/b5cea/19-08-28-3.png 1140w,\n/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/21b4d/19-08-28-3.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f49bedffdfaf4e58a7d1ea483b4a0dac/3c051/19-08-28-3.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can see that the events are displayed correctly on the calendar. For details on which keys and values to use in the events object, refer to this <a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/docs/event-object\">link</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"geteventbyid-method\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#geteventbyid-method\" aria-label=\"geteventbyid method permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>getEventById Method</h3>\n<p>You can retrieve event information using the getEventById method. Simply pass the desired ID as an argument. Let's try running <code class=\"language-text\">console.log( calendar.getEventById(1))</code> with the code above.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/21b4d/19-08-28-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.421052631578945%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/15813/19-08-28-4.webp 190w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/1cdb2/19-08-28-4.webp 380w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/9046c/19-08-28-4.webp 760w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/c89f9/19-08-28-4.webp 1140w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/af3f0/19-08-28-4.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/a2d4f/19-08-28-4.png 190w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3f520/19-08-28-4.png 380w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3c051/19-08-28-4.png 760w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/b5cea/19-08-28-4.png 1140w,\n/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/21b4d/19-08-28-4.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/3ceba0e38a372cd616fd66552da9d0f4/3c051/19-08-28-4.png\"\n            alt=\"img\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>You can see that the information for the event with 'id: 1' has been printed.</p>\n<h3 id=\"references\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references\" aria-label=\"references permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/\">FullCalendar Official Website</a><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/#demos\">Demo</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://fullcalendar.io/#demos\">\n</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#displaying-fullcalendar\">Displaying FullCalendar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#plugins\">Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#handler\">Handler</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#event-options\">Event Options</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#geteventbyid-method\">getEventById Method</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#references\">References</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/frontend/19-08-28/","title":"Displaying FullCalendar Events with Script","category":"FrontEnd","date":"2019-08-28"}}},"pageContext":{"postPath":"/frontend/19-08-28/","language":"eng","langRegex":"/contents/eng/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2145088972","256249292","63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}